::DarkMouse::

She sat there for a moment shaking. The shaking stopped and she 
looked up at Quickstrike. "Thanks. I'm still not used to this." She  
smiled at him.  "You don't have to stay here if you don't want to. I 
can just wait here.  Really,I'll be alright. Go and have fun."
She motioned with her hand for him to go. She was feeling really 
drained.  What little she had done had drained her of what little 
energy she had.  She needed to rest and she knew it. She also didn't 
want her friend to see her in this feeble state much longer. "Well, 
go on, I'll be ok."  the shaking started again.
